    <item>
      <title>英国和爱尔兰领导人就移民潮发生冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/uk-ireland-leaders-on-collision-course-over-migration-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国和爱尔兰之间因寻求庇护者激增而发生的争端有可能颠覆两国本已脆弱的关系。随着两国领导人选举即将到来，双方似乎都不会做出让步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/uk-ireland-leaders-on-collision-course-over-migration-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油资源丰富的乍得军政府领导人有望在与美国关系紧张之际赢得选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/chad-junta-leader-mahamat-deby-set-to-win-presidential-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乍得军事统治者穆罕默德·代比几乎肯定会赢得该国 5 月 6 日的总统选举，从而巩固执政军政府的权力，此举可能会危及美国在该地区军事参与的未来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/chad-junta-leader-mahamat-deby-set-to-win-presidential-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱荷华州驱逐法因越权而受到美国起诉的威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/iowa-deportation-law-draws-threat-to-sue-from-us-as-overreach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府告诉爱荷华州，它将提起诉讼，阻止一项新法律，该法律将被驱逐出境后重新进入该州视为犯罪，称该法律受到联邦法律的先发制人，破坏了对外关系，并实际上创建了第二个移民制度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/iowa-deportation-law-draws-threat-to-sue-from-us-as-overreach</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 22:18:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普封口费案审判：第二周证词的关键要点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/trump-hush-money-trial-key-takeaways-from-week-two-of-testimony</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)封口费刑事审判的第二周证词让陪审员们掌握了有关向两名女性付款的谈判的第一手资料，以及这位前总统的2016年竞选团队在她们所谓的婚外情消息泄露后的反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/trump-hush-money-trial-key-takeaways-from-week-two-of-testimony</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 21:30:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普助手希克斯在证人席上哭泣，回忆2016年的混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/trump-aide-hicks-cries-on-witness-stand-recalls-campaign-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的前高级助手霍普·希克斯 (Hope Hicks) 星期五在证人席上哭泣，他在对 2016 年竞选活动因详细描述这位前总统涉嫌婚外情的爆炸性故事而感到恐慌的证词后，在证人席上哭泣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/trump-aide-hicks-cries-on-witness-stand-recalls-campaign-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 21:00:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
