      <title>美国司法部将于 5 月 28 日决定波音是否违反起诉协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/doj-to-decide-if-boeing-breached-prosecution-deal-by-may-28</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据发送给受害者家属律师的一封电子邮件，美国司法部计划在 5 月 28 日之前决定波音公司是否违反了该公司为逃避与两架 737 Max 飞机坠毁相关的刑事指控而达成的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/doj-to-decide-if-boeing-breached-prosecution-deal-by-may-28</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 19:05:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
